    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "A really appealing, good-condition car that\u2019s easy to like and priced where it should be. It shows well overall, has been kept in respectable shape, and offers the kind of clean, usable presentation that makes it a fun and satisfying driver. Not a showpiece, but a genuinely solid example for someone who wants a nice car they can enjoy right away.",
