    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Well-kept, honest car in good condition that presents nicely and is ready to enjoy. It has clearly been cared for, shows normal age-appropriate wear, and offers a great mix of comfort, value, and everyday dependability. Clean overall, attractive inside and out, and a solid choice for someone looking for a quality vehicle without paying mint-condition money.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition example that presents well overall and should satisfy a buyer looking for a nice driver rather than a trailer queen. The body, paint, and trim show well at a glance, with the expected light cosmetic wear, minor imperfections, and signs of normal use you\u2019d expect from a car that has been enjoyed and maintained. The interior is tidy and complete, showing some age and use but nothing out of line for a well-kept car in this category. Overall, this is a solid, attractive car you can feel good about using and showing, with the right balance of presentation and realism.",
      "price": 33900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Fair-condition driver that looks complete and usable, but it shows clear age and wear throughout. Expect older paint with noticeable imperfections, tired trim in places, and an interior that is presentable but worn from use. This is not a show car or a freshly restored example; it\u2019s the kind of car you buy to enjoy as-is while improving over time. A buyer should expect a solid driver with cosmetic needs and the possibility of some ongoing maintenance or sorting that comes with an honest, older car.",
      "price": 19800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "Poor condition. This car shows significant wear inside and out and will need repairs and reconditioning. Expect cosmetic flaws, noticeable age, and mechanical needs. Best suited for a buyer looking for a project, parts, or basic transportation with work.",
      "price": 5900.0,
